&lt;a href="markets.qmd" class="cta-button"&gt;Find Us at the Market&lt;/a&gt;




Rooted in Family, Grown with Love


Schenone Farms is a small, family-owned cherry farm located in Linden, California. For generations, we’ve brought the best of the harvest to local markets. From our trees to your table—freshness and tradition you can taste.




Cherry Season is Here!


Join us every weekend in May, June, and early July at farmers markets across San Diego. We bring fresh-picked cherries directly from the farm to you!
